rows.label: qst712101_msg0001
rows.name:
You've come... As expected of
those who cleared our tests.

rows.label: qst712101_msg0002
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Think ]Mo mo... Wh-what should I do, mo...

rows.label: qst712101_msg0003
rows.name:
So, in your opinion, do you
think we can be of service
on this dangerous mission?

rows.label: qst712101_msg0004
rows.name: Yes, about that...

rows.label: qst712101_msg0005
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ] I-in that case, I have to think of
a way to make them give up, mo...

rows.label: qst712101_msg0006
rows.name:
You already know our skills.
What's the problem?

rows.label: qst712101_msg0007
rows.name:
J-just one more time! I want to
test you just one more time, mo!

rows.label: qst712101_msg0008
rows.name: ...is what he insists on. My apologies.

rows.label: qst712101_msg0009
rows.name: My, my, what a predicament.

rows.label: qst712101_msg0010
rows.name:
This is the last test, mo! This
time, it's a summation of all the
tests so far, mo! The content is...

rows.label: qst712101_msg0011
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Think ] What to do, mo... what to do, mo...

rows.label: qst712101_msg0012
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Think ] Mo! I've got it, mo!

rows.label: qst712101_msg0013
rows.name:
10 Fusion Combos! I want
you to pull that off, mo!

rows.label: qst712101_msg0014
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ] This is it, mo! With this,
they're sure to give up
halfway through, mo!

rows.label: qst712101_msg0015
rows.name: I see... Interesting.

rows.label: qst712101_msg0016
rows.name:
You may already know this, but a Fusion
Combo is a combination of a Driver Combo
and a Blade Combo, so to speak.

rows.label: qst712101_msg0017
rows.name:
The condition is to perform a Blade
Combo during a Driver Combo, or a
Driver Combo during a Blade Combo.

rows.label: qst712101_msg0018
rows.name:
As usual, the location and opponent
don't matter. Choose a place and opponent
where you can maximize your skills.

rows.label: qst712101_msg0019
rows.name:
Indeed, this could be called a
summation of all the tests so far.

rows.label: qst712101_msg0020
rows.name:
Understood... We'll do our best
to meet your expectations.

rows.label: qst712101_msg0021
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ] Mo mo! They just accepted
it so easily, mo!

rows.label: qst712101_msg0022
rows.name:
A-ahem! Well then, once you've
performed 10 Fusion Combos, be
sure to report back, mo!

rows.label: qst712101_msg0023
rows.name:
I will see your true power...
until the very end.
